title: I just saved you $35 - Williams screwdriver hack #shorts
description:
Thanks to John Zanussi, you can hack your Williams WRS-1 Ratcheting Screwdriver to have a bonafide bitholder!

Here's the 3D file: https://www.printables.com/model/400661-williams-screwdriver-bit-holder

And my 3D Printer: https://amzn.to/3S7ZoId
And how I set up my 3D printer: https://github.com/geerlingguy/3d-printing
